{"tid":1485111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家散水啦","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:37:19.000Z","uid":24424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8e83440c9637f408b16bebae200e322cf157ac","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"今日陪發夢同一班手足行完 求下所有人走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日和理非一日 交返個波比國際 政府 下次民陣先有牙力再叫人出 <br />\n<br />\n求下大家唔好將今日香港人嘅努力白費 我明白前線手足可能好想難得有咁多人 不如咁多人一齊做野 但今日真係不宜呀 他日有野做 小弟同你地一齊出<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢 返到屋企洗腳 大家都係真心愛香港嘅香港人"},{"pid":"c80e4039351759a3c2a82c1f2b536d6365d75fe2","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa786277a5407143216a6284e8cd42db8581978c","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43140d46576be10dd624900d592e19863620cd99","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34487e22b01a7f7638802bec30a629891956145e","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46e815da0e1cae3c4e9d758be4c68d94cc109c0a","tid":1485111,"uid":55833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47670ba0b0ad2922b98cdc67ee3a2ed6b2592167","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef3c870f03b003c7c022d47be7438c5b1a617b87","tid":1485111,"uid":24424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ea082754426f61def19469ae4331609d9b85831","tid":1485111,"uid":14024